description:
Currently, Modus Web components doesn't provide a way to customize styling for its components because it uses shadow DOM mode, and the code inside shadow DOM is encapsulated which cannot be styled from outside. 
So we need custom properties that can penetrate the shadow DOM.

@ryan-henness-trimble @jeffdoolittle @coliff please correct me if am wrong.

